slim_seo.title: My Night in 9: Miss Moço - The Drake
slim_seo.description: My Night in Nine is a series where we ask some of our friends, collaborators, and all-around creatives to show us what a night at The Drake looks like for them in nine photos. Miss Moço [mo-su], of Canada’s Drag Race fame, has garnered quite an entourage. For the past 9+ years, drag brunch enthusiasts have flocked to various venues to be roused by the brunch scene queen. Outside of Drag, Moço (he/him), can be found behind the camera as a photographer where his deep love for travel, endless pursuit of self discovery and innate desire to explore human connection are the muses of his work.
